    • Method Detail

      • getTypeAppointReport

        static java.lang.String getTypeAppointReport()
                                      throws java.sql.SQLException
        This method will create a monthly summary report. I used Lambda expression Consumer in foreach() method to create a key string in "Month - Appointment type" format. And use it in Hashmap result as key values. It will add new key to the result if there is no matching key in the Map or increment the value by 1 if there is a match.
        Returns:
        monthly summary report
        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException
